<subSubSection id="C368652E93518E0CF2FAF8C5FBC3F872" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593518E0CF2FAF8C5FC48F85E" blockId="8.[151,1436,1807,1977]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">
Designation is based on the first specimens mentioned in the description. Keys to identify this species are found in 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493518E0CF289F8E9FE85F85E" author="Fuente de la, J. M." box="[180,340,1915,1941]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" refId="ref10490" refString="Fuente de la, J. M. (1927) Tablas analiticas para la clasificacion de los coleopteros de la Peninsula Iberica. Adephaga: I Cicindelidae, II Carabidae. J. Bosch, Barcelona, 415 pp." type="book" year="1927">Fuente (1927)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493518E0CF35DF8E9FDD9F85E" author="Jeannel, R." box="[352,520,1915,1941]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" pagination="572 - 1173" refId="ref11231" refString="Jeannel, R. (1942) Coleopteres carabiques. Deuxieme partie. Faune de France 40. Librairie de la Faculte des Sciences, Paris, pp. 572 - 1173." type="book chapter" year="1942">Jeannel (1942)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493518E0CF02FF8E9FD6FF85E" author="Antoine, M." box="[530,702,1914,1941]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" pagination="315 - 465" refId="ref10238" refString="Antoine, M. (1959) Coleopteres Carabiques du Maroc. Troisieme partie. Memoires de la Societe des Sciences Naturelles et Physiques du Maroc, Nouvelle Serie, Zoologie, 6, 315 - 465." type="journal article" year="1959">Antoine (1959)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493518E0CF0C9F8E9FC44F85E" author="Sciaky, R." box="[756,917,1915,1941]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" pagination="29 - 120" refId="ref12184" refString="Sciaky, R. (1987) Revisione delle specie paleartiche occidentali del genere Ophonus Dejean, 1821. Memoria della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 65, 29 - 120." type="journal article" year="1987">Sciaky (1987)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593518E0CF2FAF80DFBC3F872" blockId="8.[151,1436,1807,1977]" box="[199,1042,1951,1977]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">
It has almost the same distribution as 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693518E0CF050F80DFBDFF872" authority="(Kataev &amp; Wrase, 2017 c)" baseAuthorityName="Kataev &amp; Wrase" baseAuthorityYear="2017" box="[621,1038,1951,1977]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Ophonus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pumilio">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793518E0CF050F80DFD37F872" box="[621,742,1951,1977]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="492">O. pumilio</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493518E0CF0C9F80DFBD4F872" author="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W." box="[756,1029,1951,1977]" pageId="8" pageNumber="492" pagination="1810" refId="ref11718" refString="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (2017 c) Subtribe Harpalina Bonelli, 1810. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Lobl, D. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Vol. 1. Revised and Updated Edition. Brill, Leiden, pp. 515 - 562." type="book chapter" year="2017">Kataev &amp; Wrase, 2017c</bibRefCitation>
